dct_title_s: Insulae et arcis Mocambique descriptio ad fines Melinde sita ebano puriss
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially and by shading.
Decorative cartouche, crowned shield, compass rose, rhumb lines, buildings, ships and boats, figures, vegetation.
German text in cartouche, below title.
